    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突击队武器与皮肤礼包是《Sniper Elite: Resistance》的免费内容更新包，为你的武器库增添了致命的DL卡宾枪和隐蔽精英步枪伪装罩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003630/extras/58ef574f9108e2d99d3ee94ab5da51c2.poster.avif?t=1745931478\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003630/extras/58ef574f9108e2d99d3ee94ab5da51c2.webm?t=1745931478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003630/extras/58ef574f9108e2d99d3ee94ab5da51c2.mp4?t=1745931478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >D.L.卡宾枪是一款消音步枪，静音效果极佳，是盟军突击队的主要武器。DL卡宾枪与隐蔽精英步枪伪装罩堪称绝配，后者能大幅提升精英特工在最危险的秘密任务中的隐蔽能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突击队武器与皮肤礼包包含：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-\tD.L.卡宾枪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-\t隐蔽精英步枪伪装罩</p>",
